data.description: Luxurious single-story living awaits! Stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bath craftsman style home just MONTHS old and LOADED with upgrades. The gourmet kitchen offers quartz countertops with an 8’ island, farmhouse sink and nickel-plated gooseneck faucet. Soft close drawers, pull out pan shelving, separate pantry, and stainless-steel appliances. True LVP flooring and 9’ ceilings throughout, complimented by recess lighting. Natural light abounds in the open floorplan with oversized windows. Generous owner’s suite with ceramic tile tub surround, glass shower doors and ample walk-in closet. The third bedroom/flex space currently serves as an in-home office. Finished two car garage with custom shelving. The exterior offers an inviting covered patio with adjacent open patio ideal for relaxation and entertaining. Stone-front elevation, fresh landscaping, and manicured lawn with irrigation. Remainder of the builder warranty will transfer to the buyer. The Wood Creek Community is minutes from tax free shopping and lies in the blue-ribbon Delmar School District. Amenities include a pool, clubhouse, exercise room and walking/biking trails. Schedule your showing for this one of a kind gem before it’s too late!  Wood Creek HOA documents can be viewed at Woodcreekmd.com. Watch our video tour for more details!
